# {{IME_PROJEKTA}} - Tier 0 Security Operations Center

## _traceability
- requirement: ZAH-SEC-001 Tier 0 SOC z popolnim Red & Blue team
- design: DSN-SEC-001 Referenčna implementacija nacionalnega varnostnega centra
- test: TST-SEC-001 Verifikacija Tier 0 SOC primera

## Opis

Tier 0 Security Operations Center je najvišji nivo varnostnega operativnega centra z popolnimi zmogljivostmi za Red Team, Blue Team, Threat Intelligence, Malware Analysis, Forensics, SIGINT, FININT, OSINT in vse specializirane varnostne operacije.

## Vključene komponente

### Red Team Operations
- Reconnaissance in OSINT
- Vulnerability scanning
- Exploitation frameworks
- Persistence mechanisms
- Lateral movement
- Command & Control (C2)
- Data exfiltration

### Blue Team Operations
- SIEM/SOC monitoring
- Threat detection
- Incident response
- Forensic analysis
- Threat hunting
- Vulnerability management

### Threat Intelligence
- STIX/TAXII integration
- Threat feeds aggregation
- IOC management
- Attribution analysis
- Campaign tracking

### Malware Analysis
- Static analysis
- Dynamic analysis
- Behavioral analysis
- Code reconstruction
- Reverse engineering

### Forensics
- Device forensics
- Memory forensics
- Network forensics
- Disk forensics
- Mobile forensics

### Intelligence Operations
- SIGINT (Signals Intelligence)
- FININT (Financial Intelligence)
- OSINT (Open Source Intelligence)
- HUMINT (Human Intelligence)
- Counter-Intelligence

### Visualization
- 2D real-time dashboards
- 3D network topology
- Attack path visualization
- Threat landscape maps

### Stealth & Anti-Forensics
- Covert operations
- Evidence destruction
- Evasion techniques
- Counter-surveillance

## Skladnost

- DO-178C DAL-A
- IEC-61508 SIL-4
- ISO-26262 ASIL-D
- MIL-STD-882E
- NIST 800-53
- ISO 27001
