## Zagon

```bash
npm install
npm run build
npm run soc:start
npm run soc:monitor
```

## Konfiguracija

Vsa konfiguracija je v `config/soc-config.yaml`:

```yaml
soc:
  tier: 0
  classification: TOP_SECRET
  operations:
    red_team: enabled
    blue_team: enabled
    threat_intel: enabled
    malware_analysis: enabled
    forensics: enabled
    sigint: enabled
    finint: enabled
    osint: enabled
    counter_intel: enabled
  visualization:
    2d_dashboards: enabled
    3d_topology: enabled
    real_time: enabled
  stealth:
    covert_ops: enabled
    anti_forensics: enabled
```

